					<common:class level="1">Inorganic chemicals</common:class>
				</common:classification>
			</classificationInformation>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Potassium phosphate is used to treat or prevent hypophosphatemia and is sometimes added to intravenous fluids. It is also used as a food additive to preserve and extend the shelf life of processed foods, and as a reagent with high buffering capacity in various applications, including the culture of microorganisms and in phosphate buffered saline (PBS). It occurs in monobasic, dibasic, and tribasic forms, with tribasic potassium phosphate being denoted as K3PO4.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">磷酸钾用于治疗或预防低磷血症，有时也加入静脉输液中。它还被用作食品添加剂，以保存和延长加工食品的保质期，并在各种应用中作为具有高缓冲能力的试剂，包括微生物培养和磷酸盐缓冲盐水（PBS）中。它以一元、二元和三元形式存在，三元磷酸钾表示为K3PO4。</common:generalComment>
